game.name: Ice Princess Twins Birth
game.description:
Wow! This cute and beautiful Ice Princess is going to witness the biggest news of her life. Hey girls, she is pregnant and is expecting to deliver twins today. Is not pretty exciting and exhilarating for the lady? But before it happens to the lady, she needs immediate medical attention. Would you come forward to take care of her during her labor pain and at the hospital? Join Ice Princess Twins Birth and be prepared to make sure that everything goes well on this big day of her life!

When you click the play button, you would the princess sitting on her couch comfortably. Suddenly she starts feeling the labor pain in her stomach. The first thing you have to do in such a situation is to call the ambulance at 911. Now get ready to take care of everything before the ambulance arrives in this one of the best HTML5 doctor games. Try to make her claim with the help of items you see on the table lying in front of her! Hydrate her body with some water and call for her husband to give her a relaxing kiss or hug!

Your job is not done here. Become her helping hand when she is in the hospital with her newly born cute babies in this medical simulation game! Change their diapers, measure their weight and even make the arrangement for some milk for the twins! Do not ignore the health of this beautiful mommy and make sure that she takes her vitamins on time. Try to provide the best hospital care to the three and help them to leave the hospital happily so that she can start a new life with her lovely kids perfectly! Try out more medical simulators on our website for free without download!
